{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Beverly Joubert: We are truly passionate"},{"time":2000,"text":"about the African wilderness"},{"time":4000,"text":"and protecting the African wilderness,"},{"time":6000,"text":"and so what we've done"},{"time":8000,"text":"is we've focused on iconic cats."},{"time":11000,"text":"And I know,"},{"time":13000,"text":"in the light of human suffering and poverty"},{"time":15000,"text":"and even climate change,"},{"time":17000,"text":"one would wonder,"},{"time":19000,"text":"why worry about a few cats?"},{"time":22000,"text":"Well today we're here"},{"time":24000,"text":"to share with you a message that we have learned"},{"time":26000,"text":"from a very important and special character --"},{"time":29000,"text":"this leopard."}]},{"cues":[{"time":31000,"text":"Dereck Joubert: Well, our lives have basically been"},{"time":34000,"text":"like a super long episode of \"CSI\" --"},{"time":36000,"text":"something like 28 years."},{"time":39000,"text":"In essence, what we've done"},{"time":41000,"text":"is we've studied the science, we've looked at the behavior,"},{"time":43000,"text":"we've seen over 2,000 kills"},{"time":45000,"text":"by these amazing animals."},{"time":48000,"text":"But one of the things that science really lets us down on"},{"time":51000,"text":"is that personality,"},{"time":53000,"text":"that individual personality that these animals have."},{"time":57000,"text":"And here's a prime example."},{"time":59000,"text":"We found this leopard in a 2,000-year-old"},{"time":61000,"text":"baobab tree in Africa,"},{"time":63000,"text":"the same tree that we found her mother in"},{"time":65000,"text":"and her grandmother."},{"time":67000,"text":"And she took us on a journey"},{"time":70000,"text":"and revealed something very special to us --"},{"time":73000,"text":"her own daughter, eight days old."},{"time":75000,"text":"And the minute we found this leopard,"},{"time":77000,"text":"we realized that we needed to move in,"},{"time":79000,"text":"and so we basically stayed with this leopard"},{"time":81000,"text":"for the next four-and-a-half years --"},{"time":83000,"text":"following her every day,"},{"time":85000,"text":"getting to know her,"},{"time":87000,"text":"that individual personality of hers,"},{"time":89000,"text":"and really coming to know her."},{"time":91000,"text":"Now I'm destined"},{"time":94000,"text":"to spend a lot of time"},{"time":96000,"text":"with some unique,"},{"time":98000,"text":"very, very special,"},{"time":100000,"text":"individualistic"},{"time":102000,"text":"and often seductive female characters."},{"time":105000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":107000,"text":"Beverly's clearly one of them,"},{"time":110000,"text":"and this little leopard, Legadema, is another,"},{"time":113000,"text":"and she changed our lives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":115000,"text":"BJ: Well we certainly did spend a lot of time with her --"},{"time":118000,"text":"in fact, more time than even her mother did."},{"time":120000,"text":"When her mother would go off hunting,"},{"time":122000,"text":"we would stay and film."},{"time":124000,"text":"And early on, a lightning bolt hit a tree"},{"time":127000,"text":"20 paces away from us."},{"time":129000,"text":"It was frightening,"},{"time":131000,"text":"and it showered us with leaves and a pungent smell."},{"time":134000,"text":"And of course, we were stunned for a while,"},{"time":136000,"text":"but when we managed to get our wits about us,"},{"time":139000,"text":"we looked at it and said, \"My gosh,"},{"time":141000,"text":"what's going to happen with that little cub?"},{"time":143000,"text":"She's probably going to forever associate"},{"time":145000,"text":"that deafening crash with us.\""},{"time":148000,"text":"Well, we needn't have worried."},{"time":150000,"text":"She came charging out of the thicket straight towards us,"},{"time":153000,"text":"sat next to us, shivering,"},{"time":156000,"text":"with her back towards Dereck, and looking out."},{"time":159000,"text":"And actually from that day on,"},{"time":161000,"text":"she's been comfortable with us."},{"time":163000,"text":"So we felt that that day"},{"time":165000,"text":"was the day that she really earned her name."},{"time":167000,"text":"We called her Legadema,"},{"time":169000,"text":"which means, \"light from the sky.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":172000,"text":"DJ: Now we've found these individualisms"},{"time":174000,"text":"in all sorts of animals,"},{"time":176000,"text":"in particular in the cats."},{"time":178000,"text":"This particular one is called Eetwidomayloh,"},{"time":180000,"text":"\"he who greets with fire,\""},{"time":182000,"text":"and you can just see that about him, you know -- that's his character."},{"time":185000,"text":"But only by getting up close to these animals"},{"time":187000,"text":"and spending time with them"},{"time":189000,"text":"can we actually even reach out"},{"time":191000,"text":"and dig out these personal characters that they have."}]},{"cues":[{"time":193000,"text":"BJ: But through our investigation,"},{"time":195000,"text":"we have to seek the wildest places in Africa."},{"time":198000,"text":"And right now this is in the Okavango Delta"},{"time":200000,"text":"in Botswana."},{"time":202000,"text":"Yes, it is swamp. We live in the swamp in a tent,"},{"time":205000,"text":"but I must tell you, every day is exhilarating."},{"time":208000,"text":"But also, our hearts are in our throats"},{"time":210000,"text":"a huge amount of the time,"},{"time":212000,"text":"because we're driving through water,"},{"time":214000,"text":"and it's an unknown territory."},{"time":216000,"text":"But we're really there"},{"time":218000,"text":"seeking and searching and filming the iconic cats."}]},{"cues":[{"time":221000,"text":"DJ: Now one of the big things, of course,"},{"time":223000,"text":"everybody knows that cats hate water,"},{"time":226000,"text":"and so this was a real revelation for us."},{"time":228000,"text":"And we could only find this by pushing ourselves,"},{"time":231000,"text":"by going where no sane person should go --"},{"time":236000,"text":"not without some prompting, by the way, from Beverly --"},{"time":239000,"text":"and just pushing the envelope,"},{"time":241000,"text":"going out there, pushing our vehicle, pushing ourselves."},{"time":244000,"text":"But we've managed to find that these lions"},{"time":246000,"text":"are 15 percent bigger than any others,"},{"time":248000,"text":"and they specialize in hunting buffalo in the water."}]},{"cues":[{"time":252000,"text":"BJ: And then of course, the challenge"},{"time":254000,"text":"is knowing when to turn around."},{"time":257000,"text":"We don't always get that right,"},{"time":259000,"text":"and on this particular day,"},{"time":261000,"text":"we seriously underestimated the depth."},{"time":264000,"text":"We got deeper and deeper,"},{"time":266000,"text":"until it was at Dereck's chest-height."},{"time":268000,"text":"Well then we hit a deep depression,"},{"time":271000,"text":"and we seriously submerged the vehicle."},{"time":274000,"text":"We actually managed to drown"},{"time":276000,"text":"two million dollars' worth of camera gear."},{"time":279000,"text":"We drowned our pride, I must tell you,"},{"time":281000,"text":"which was really serious,"},{"time":283000,"text":"and we seized the engine."}]},{"cues":[{"time":286000,"text":"DJ: And of course, one of the rules that we have in the vehicle"},{"time":288000,"text":"is that he who drowns the vehicle"},{"time":290000,"text":"gets to swim with the crocodiles."},{"time":292000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":294000,"text":"You will notice also that all of these images here"},{"time":296000,"text":"are taken from the top angle by Beverly --"},{"time":298000,"text":"the dry top angle, by the way."},{"time":300000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":303000,"text":"But all the places we get stuck in really have great views."},{"time":306000,"text":"And it wasn't a moment, and these lions came back towards us,"},{"time":309000,"text":"and Beverly was able to get a great photograph."}]},{"cues":[{"time":311000,"text":"BJ: But we truly do"},{"time":313000,"text":"spend day and night"},{"time":315000,"text":"trying to capture unique footage."},{"time":317000,"text":"And 20 years ago,"},{"time":319000,"text":"we did a film called \"Eternal Enemies\""},{"time":321000,"text":"where we managed to capture"},{"time":323000,"text":"this unusual disturbing behavior across two species --"},{"time":326000,"text":"lions and hyenas."},{"time":328000,"text":"And surprisingly, it became a cult film."},{"time":331000,"text":"And we can only work that out"},{"time":333000,"text":"as people were seeing parallels"},{"time":335000,"text":"between the thuggish side of nature"},{"time":338000,"text":"and gang warfare."}]},{"cues":[{"time":340000,"text":"DJ: It was amazing, because you can see that this lion"},{"time":343000,"text":"is doing exactly what his name,"},{"time":345000,"text":"Eetwidomayloh, represents."},{"time":347000,"text":"He's focused on this hyena,"},{"time":349000,"text":"and he is going to get it."},{"time":352000,"text":"(Animal sounds)"},{"time":356000,"text":"But that's, I think, what this is all about,"},{"time":359000,"text":"is that these individuals have these personalities and characters."},{"time":362000,"text":"But for us to get them, not only do we push ourselves,"},{"time":365000,"text":"but we live by certain rules of engagement,"},{"time":368000,"text":"which mean we can't interfere."},{"time":370000,"text":"This sort of behavior has been going on"},{"time":372000,"text":"for three, four, five million years,"},{"time":374000,"text":"and we can't step in and say, \"That's wrong, and that's right.\""},{"time":377000,"text":"But that's not always easy for us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":380000,"text":"BJ: So, as Dereck says,"},{"time":382000,"text":"we have to work through extremes --"},{"time":384000,"text":"extreme temperatures, push ourselves at night."},{"time":386000,"text":"Sleep deprivation is extreme."},{"time":389000,"text":"We're on the edge"},{"time":391000,"text":"through a large part of the time."},{"time":393000,"text":"But, for 10 years, we tried to capture"},{"time":395000,"text":"lions and elephants together --"},{"time":398000,"text":"and never ever managed"},{"time":400000,"text":"until this particular night."},{"time":403000,"text":"And I have to tell you"},{"time":405000,"text":"that it was a disturbing night for me."},{"time":407000,"text":"I had tears rolling down my cheeks."},{"time":409000,"text":"I was shaking with anxiety,"},{"time":412000,"text":"but I knew that [I had] to capture something"},{"time":414000,"text":"that had never been seen before, had never been documented."},{"time":417000,"text":"And I do believe you should stay with us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":421000,"text":"DJ: The amazing thing about these moments --"},{"time":423000,"text":"and this is probably a highlight of our career --"},{"time":426000,"text":"is that you never know how it's going to end."},{"time":435000,"text":"Many people believe, in fact,"},{"time":437000,"text":"that death begins in the eyes, not in the heart,"},{"time":439000,"text":"not in the lungs,"},{"time":441000,"text":"and that's when people give up hope,"},{"time":443000,"text":"or when any life form gives up hope."},{"time":445000,"text":"And you can see the start of it here."},{"time":449000,"text":"This elephant, against overwhelming odds,"},{"time":452000,"text":"simply gives up hope."},{"time":466000,"text":"But by the same token,"},{"time":469000,"text":"you can get your hope back again."},{"time":473000,"text":"So just when you think it's all over, something else happens,"},{"time":476000,"text":"some spark gets into you,"},{"time":478000,"text":"some sort of will to fight --"},{"time":481000,"text":"that iron will that we all have,"},{"time":483000,"text":"that this elephant has,"},{"time":485000,"text":"that conservation has, that big cats have."},{"time":488000,"text":"Everything has that will to survive,"},{"time":491000,"text":"to fight, to push through that mental barrier"},{"time":493000,"text":"and to keep going."},{"time":496000,"text":"And for us, in many ways,"},{"time":498000,"text":"this elephant has become"},{"time":500000,"text":"a symbol of inspiration for us,"},{"time":502000,"text":"a symbol of that hope as we go forward in our work."}]},{"cues":[{"time":505000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":516000,"text":"Now back to the leopard."},{"time":518000,"text":"We were spending so much time with this leopard"},{"time":520000,"text":"and getting to understand her individualism,"},{"time":522000,"text":"her personal character,"},{"time":524000,"text":"that maybe we were taking it a little bit far."},{"time":527000,"text":"We were perhaps taking her for granted,"},{"time":529000,"text":"and maybe she didn't like that that much."},{"time":531000,"text":"This is about couples working together,"},{"time":533000,"text":"and so I do need to say that within the vehicle"},{"time":536000,"text":"we have quite strict territories, Beverly and I."},{"time":539000,"text":"Beverly sits on the one side"},{"time":541000,"text":"where all her camera gear is,"},{"time":543000,"text":"and I'm on the other side where my space is."},{"time":546000,"text":"These are precious to us, these divides."}]},{"cues":[{"time":549000,"text":"BJ: But when this little cub saw"},{"time":551000,"text":"that I had vacated my seat"},{"time":553000,"text":"and climbed to the back to get some camera gear,"},{"time":555000,"text":"she came in like a curious cat"},{"time":557000,"text":"to come and investigate."},{"time":559000,"text":"It was phenomenal, and we felt grateful"},{"time":562000,"text":"that she trusted us to that extent."},{"time":564000,"text":"But at the same time, we were concerned"},{"time":566000,"text":"that if she created this as a habit"},{"time":568000,"text":"and jumped into somebody else's car,"},{"time":570000,"text":"it might not turn out the same way --"},{"time":572000,"text":"she might get shot for that."},{"time":574000,"text":"So we knew we had to react quickly."},{"time":577000,"text":"And the only way we thought we could"},{"time":580000,"text":"without scaring her"},{"time":582000,"text":"is to try and simulate a growl like her mother would make --"},{"time":584000,"text":"a hiss and a sound."},{"time":586000,"text":"So Dereck turned on the heater fan in the car --"},{"time":588000,"text":"very innovative."}]},{"cues":[{"time":590000,"text":"DJ: It was the only way for me to save the marriage,"},{"time":592000,"text":"because Beverly felt she was being replaced, you see."},{"time":594000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":597000,"text":"But really and truly, this was how"},{"time":599000,"text":"this little leopard was displaying"},{"time":601000,"text":"her individual personality."},{"time":603000,"text":"But nothing prepared us"},{"time":605000,"text":"for what happened next in our relationship with her,"},{"time":607000,"text":"when she started hunting."}]},{"cues":[{"time":609000,"text":"BJ: And on this first hunt, we truly were excited."},{"time":612000,"text":"It was like watching a graduation ceremony."},{"time":614000,"text":"We felt like we were surrogate parents."},{"time":616000,"text":"And of course, we knew now"},{"time":618000,"text":"that she was going to survive."},{"time":620000,"text":"But only when we saw the tiny baby baboon"},{"time":623000,"text":"clinging to the mother's fur"},{"time":625000,"text":"did we realize that something very unique"},{"time":627000,"text":"was taking place here with Legadema."},{"time":630000,"text":"And of course, the baby baboon was so innocent,"},{"time":633000,"text":"it didn't turn and run."},{"time":635000,"text":"So what we watched"},{"time":637000,"text":"over the next couple of hours"},{"time":639000,"text":"was very unique."},{"time":642000,"text":"It was absolutely amazing"},{"time":644000,"text":"when she picked it up to safety,"},{"time":646000,"text":"protecting it from the hyena."},{"time":649000,"text":"And over the next five hours,"},{"time":652000,"text":"she took care of it."},{"time":654000,"text":"We realized that we actually don't know everything,"},{"time":657000,"text":"and that nature is so unpredictable,"},{"time":661000,"text":"we have to be open at all times."}]},{"cues":[{"time":664000,"text":"DJ: Okay, so she was a little bit rough."},{"time":666000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":671000,"text":"But in fact,"},{"time":675000,"text":"what we were seeing here was interesting."},{"time":678000,"text":"Because she is a cub wanting to play,"},{"time":681000,"text":"but she was also a predator needing to kill,"},{"time":684000,"text":"and yet conflicted in some way,"},{"time":686000,"text":"because she was also an emerging mother."},{"time":689000,"text":"She had this maternal instinct,"},{"time":691000,"text":"much like a young girl on her way to womanhood,"},{"time":695000,"text":"and so this really took us to this new level"},{"time":698000,"text":"of understanding that personality."}]},{"cues":[{"time":703000,"text":"BJ: And of course, through the night, they lay together."},{"time":706000,"text":"They ended up sleeping for hours."},{"time":708000,"text":"But I have to tell you --"},{"time":710000,"text":"everybody always asks, \"What happened to the baby baboon?\""},{"time":712000,"text":"It did die,"},{"time":714000,"text":"and we suspect it was from the freezing winter nights."}]},{"cues":[{"time":718000,"text":"DJ: So at this stage, I guess,"},{"time":720000,"text":"we had very, very firm ideas"},{"time":722000,"text":"on what conservation meant."},{"time":724000,"text":"We had to deal with these individual personalities."},{"time":727000,"text":"We had to deal with them with respect"},{"time":730000,"text":"and celebrate them."},{"time":732000,"text":"And so we, with the National Geographic, formed the Big Cats Initiative"},{"time":735000,"text":"to march forward into conservation,"},{"time":737000,"text":"taking care of the big cats that we loved --"},{"time":739000,"text":"and then had an opportunity to look back over the last 50 years"},{"time":742000,"text":"to see how well we had all collectively been doing."},{"time":745000,"text":"So when Beverly and I were born,"},{"time":747000,"text":"there were 450,000 lions,"},{"time":749000,"text":"and today there are 20,000."},{"time":752000,"text":"Tigers haven't fared any better --"},{"time":754000,"text":"45,000"},{"time":756000,"text":"down to maybe 3,000."}]},{"cues":[{"time":758000,"text":"BJ: And then cheetahs have crashed"},{"time":760000,"text":"all the way down to 12,000."},{"time":762000,"text":"Leopards have plummeted"},{"time":764000,"text":"from 700,000"},{"time":766000,"text":"down to a mere 50,000."},{"time":768000,"text":"Now in the extraordinary time"},{"time":770000,"text":"that we have worked with Legadema --"},{"time":772000,"text":"which is really over a five-year period --"},{"time":774000,"text":"10,000 leopards were legally shot"},{"time":777000,"text":"by safari hunters."},{"time":779000,"text":"And that's not the only leopards"},{"time":781000,"text":"that were being killed through that period."},{"time":783000,"text":"There's an immense amount of poaching as well,"},{"time":786000,"text":"and so possibly the same amount."},{"time":788000,"text":"It's simply not sustainable."},{"time":790000,"text":"We admire them,"},{"time":792000,"text":"and we fear them,"},{"time":794000,"text":"and yet, as man, we want to steal their power."},{"time":799000,"text":"It used to be the time"},{"time":801000,"text":"where only kings wore a leopard skin,"},{"time":804000,"text":"but now throughout rituals and ceremonies,"},{"time":806000,"text":"traditional healers and ministers."},{"time":809000,"text":"And of course, looking at this lion paw"},{"time":812000,"text":"that has been skinned,"},{"time":814000,"text":"it eerily reminds me"},{"time":816000,"text":"of a human hand,"},{"time":818000,"text":"and that's ironic, because their fate is in our hands."}]},{"cues":[{"time":821000,"text":"DJ: There's a burgeoning bone trade."},{"time":823000,"text":"South Africa just released some lion bones onto the market."},{"time":826000,"text":"Lion bones and tiger bones look exactly the same,"},{"time":829000,"text":"and so in a stroke, the lion bone industry"},{"time":832000,"text":"is going to wipe out all the tigers."},{"time":835000,"text":"So we have a real problem here,"},{"time":837000,"text":"no more so than the lions do, the male lions."},{"time":840000,"text":"So the 20,000 lion figure that you just saw"},{"time":843000,"text":"is actually a red herring,"},{"time":845000,"text":"because there may be 3,000 or 4,000 male lions,"},{"time":848000,"text":"and they all are actually"},{"time":850000,"text":"infected with the same disease."},{"time":852000,"text":"I call it complacency --"},{"time":854000,"text":"our complacency."},{"time":856000,"text":"Because there's a sport, there's an activity going on"},{"time":859000,"text":"that we're all aware of, that we condone."},{"time":865000,"text":"And that's probably because we haven't seen it"},{"time":867000,"text":"like we are today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":871000,"text":"BJ: And you have to know"},{"time":873000,"text":"that, when a male lion is killed,"},{"time":875000,"text":"it completely disrupts the whole pride."},{"time":878000,"text":"A new male comes into the area"},{"time":880000,"text":"and takes over the pride,"},{"time":882000,"text":"and, of course, first of all kills all the cubs"},{"time":885000,"text":"and possibly some of the females that are defending their cubs."},{"time":888000,"text":"So we've estimated"},{"time":890000,"text":"that between 20 [and] 30 lions are killed"},{"time":893000,"text":"when one lion is hanging on a wall"},{"time":896000,"text":"somewhere in a far-off place."}]},{"cues":[{"time":898000,"text":"DJ: So what our investigations have shown"},{"time":900000,"text":"is that these lions are essential."},{"time":902000,"text":"They're essential to the habitat."},{"time":904000,"text":"If they disappear,"},{"time":906000,"text":"whole ecosystems in Africa disappear."},{"time":909000,"text":"There's an 80-billion-dollar-a-year"},{"time":911000,"text":"ecotourism revenue stream into Africa."},{"time":914000,"text":"So this is not just a concern about lions;"},{"time":917000,"text":"it's a concern about communities in Africa as well."},{"time":920000,"text":"If they disappear, all of that goes away."},{"time":923000,"text":"But what I'm more concerned about in many ways"},{"time":926000,"text":"is that, as we de-link ourselves from nature,"},{"time":929000,"text":"as we de-link ourselves spiritually"},{"time":931000,"text":"from these animals,"},{"time":933000,"text":"we lose hope,"},{"time":936000,"text":"we lose that spiritual connection,"},{"time":939000,"text":"our dignity, that thing within us"},{"time":942000,"text":"that keeps us connected to the planet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":944000,"text":"BJ: So you have to know, looking into the eyes"},{"time":947000,"text":"of lions and leopards right now,"},{"time":950000,"text":"it is all about critical awareness."},{"time":952000,"text":"And so what we are doing,"},{"time":954000,"text":"in February, we're bringing out a film called \"The Last Lion,\""},{"time":957000,"text":"and \"The Last Lion\" is exactly"},{"time":959000,"text":"what is happening right now."},{"time":961000,"text":"That is the situation we're in --"},{"time":963000,"text":"the last lions."},{"time":965000,"text":"That is, if we don't take action and do something,"},{"time":967000,"text":"these plains will be completely devoid"},{"time":969000,"text":"of big cats,"},{"time":971000,"text":"and then, in turn, everything else will disappear."},{"time":974000,"text":"And simply, if we can't protect them,"},{"time":976000,"text":"we're going to have a job protecting ourselves as well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":979000,"text":"DJ: And in fact, that original thing that we spoke about"},{"time":982000,"text":"and designed our lives by --"},{"time":984000,"text":"that conservation was all about respect"},{"time":986000,"text":"and celebration --"},{"time":988000,"text":"is probably true. That's really what it needs."},{"time":991000,"text":"We need it. We respect and celebrate each other"},{"time":994000,"text":"as a man and a woman, as a community"},{"time":997000,"text":"and as part of this planet,"},{"time":999000,"text":"and we need to continue that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1001000,"text":"And Legadema?"},{"time":1003000,"text":"Well we can report, in fact,"},{"time":1005000,"text":"that we're grandparents."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1007000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1009000,"text":"BJ/DJ: Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1011000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}